{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1683-06_059","@resp":"nbb","head":{"#1":{"value":"Galanterie de M","id":"/div/head/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/head/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de Ligniere, à un jeune Seigneur Anglois","id":"/div/head/#2"}},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1683 [tome 6], p. 59-63.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"La Galanterie qui suit porte sa recommandation aupres de vous, par le nom de son Autheur, dont je sçay que vous estimez tous les Ouvrages. On en voit peu dont le tour soit si aisé. Aussi sont-ils approuvez de tout le monde.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"GALANTERIE","id":"/div/quote/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE M","id":"/div/quote/label/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/quote/label/#[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" DE LIGNIERE,","id":"/div/quote/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"A un jeune Seigneur Anglois.","id":"/div/quote/label/#[6]/#"}}]},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On me demande un Compliment","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour deux Sujets pleins d’agrément.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le bel Enfant qui vient de naître,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour leur bonheur, nous fait connaître","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’ils sont de charmans Ouvriers,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qu’ils méritent des Lauriers ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car si l’on donne des Couronnes","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ceux qui dans les Champs guerriers","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont tué beaucoup de Personnes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On doit plutost à pleine main","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En donner à qui s’évertuë","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De reparer le Genre-humain,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à celuy qui blesse, &amp; qui tuë.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Milord, vous estes un Héros,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis que vos Exploits en champ clos","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Valent mieux que ceux de la Guerre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ne font qu’atrister la Terre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par une infinité de maux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est avec raison qu’on vous aime,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez un mérite extréme,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous m’avez paru fort adroit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous plaisez dés qu’on vous voit.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’aplaudissois sur la Barriere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand vous fournissiez la Carriere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chez Longpré, qui n’a point d’égal","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans l’Art de monter à cheval ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce noble Ecuyer vous estime,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous estes, dit-il, un Seigneur","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus qu’aucun autre magnanime,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vostre vertu fait honneur","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A vostre Païs maritime.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plusieurs en parlent comme luy,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’est pas le seul qui vous vante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui fasse cas aujourd’huy","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vostre Personne excellente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de vostre Race éclatante.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Homme le moins habile sçait","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’Histoire Angloise s’honore","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du fameux nom de Sommerset,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de Northumbelland encore.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous estes un Couple parfait ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Ciel toûjours vous benisse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que rien ne vous des-unisse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est le souhait d’un Malheureux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ce Malheureux est Ligniere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui de la plus humble maniere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ose vous salüer tous deux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nostre bon Amy Rasigade,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui sans nulle triste boutade","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous a mieux instruit que Chiron","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’éleva le vaillant Achille,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous dira que j’ay quelque nom,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans estre Homere, ny Virgile,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que parmy les beaux Esprits","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On me regarde sans mépris.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}}]}}}}